descriptions: You can download a trial version of this app to try it for 15 minutes for free.
You won’t be charged anything when this free trial ends. You can’t make in-app purchases or use add-on content during this free trial, but you’ll keep any achievements you earn.

display_long_description:
AAA Sailor allows you to drive a variety of boats, yachts, and ships, and provides a realistic experience.

1. Boat racing function
2. Free boat driving practice
3. Submarine driving, torpedo launching function
4. Aircraft carrier driving and air fighter driving
5. Medieval warship driving and cannon operation
6. Various fish fishing
7. Rowing, sailing and lowering

Advanced graphic technology is applied to maximize the realistic feeling.
